questiondata.strat-other: In case "visuallizing" didn't exactly convey what I was doing I was creating a scene that contained all the words to the best of my ability.  Like when I heard guitar, stallion, cacoon, silkworm velvet I'd imagine a horse with a velvet saddle with a guitar strung over it with a silkworm cacoon hanging off that.
